Good For Dogs - Foster Care Database
====================================

## Helping shelters and rescue groups save more lives

This software is intended to assist those providing care to orphaned animals by
putting them in foster care.


## Installation instructions

# Clone git repository

  git clone git@github.com:mbailey/ls.git

# Setup local database

  cd ls
  cp config/database.yml-example config/database.yml
  edit config/database.yml
  rake db:create
  rake db:schema:load

# Install gems using bundler [http://github.com/wycats/bundler]

  sudo gem install bundler
  gem bundle --cached

# Run the app 

  http://ls.local/ under Passenger or localhost:3000 using ./script/server



